title: Cozy Powell - 'Best Of' [192k MP3]
description:
Cozy Powell - RIP

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Personnel includes: [Former Ritchie Blackmore's Rainbow, Black Sabbath, Michael Schenker Group, ELP drummer] Cozy Powell (drums, tubular bells, handbells, gong, tympani, snare, percussion); Jeff Beck, Gary Moore, Dave Clempson, Bernie Marsden, Mel Galley (guitar); Don Airey (piano, keyboards, Moog, mini-Moog, synthesizer); John Cook (keyboards); Max Middleton (Moog, Fender Rhodes); Jon Lord (keyboards); David Sancious (synthesizer); Jack Bruce, Colin Hodgkinson (bass); John Du Prez, The Philharmonia.

Producers: Martin Birch, Cozy Powell, Guy Birdmead, Nick Griffiths.

Compilation producer: Bill Levenson.

All tracks have been digitally remastered.
